Warrior of the 36th Season<br>
Third Elder of <a href=http://www.webhazard.net>The Tears of Veeshan<a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/umirahze521.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mirahze521</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tears of Veeshan</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/27/01 9:26:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Salvia's Quest</span><hr size=1> &lt;Salvia listens intently to Tigonies side of the story.  After her friend finishes the tale(she thinks Tigonie has quite a way with words) Salvia refills Tigonie's glass of honey mead and tells of what happened after she heard the battle raging on the first floor)<br>
<br>
<br>
I cried for Tigonie and the others to hurry.  I screamed of what they were trying to do.  Tigonie seemed astounded at the thought of a coerced wood elf.  She evn shouted that it could not be done.  I told her that she should tell them that.&lt;winks at Tigonie&gt;<br>
<br>
Unfortunately, the brave souls who had come to rescue me came too late.  The Overseer brought the amulet to me, holding it close to my arm.  He spoke a few more broken phrases and all went black.  I have no memory of what happened after that.  <br>
<br>
But now that I have heard Tigonie's side I am most grieved at my actions. <br>
<br>
&lt;looks sadly at Tigonie&gt;<br>
<br>
&quot;I am sorry for how I acted my friend.  I cannot believe I attacked you like that. Please forgive me&quot;<br>
<br>
&lt;lowers her head&gt;<br>
<br>
The next thing I remember is waking up on the ground.  I felt weak, my strength and mana drained away from me.  I could barely move.  I was surrounded by faces, strange and familiar alike.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Where am I?&quot; I whispered,&quot; What has happened?&quot;<br>
<br>
Tigonie gave me a quick explanation, just enough for me to grasp what had happened. I was helped to my feet by a pair of strong arms.  All around me people were smiling, and a small hand broke through the crowd, offering me a cookie to raise my spirits.<br>
<br>
I smiled and tears welled in my eyes.<br>
<br>
&quot;Thank you everyone,&quot; I sniffled,&quot; I shall be forever in your debt.&quot;<br>
<br>
A handsome high elf in the group nodded my way and said, &quot;We were only too happy to help.&quot;  I was then introduced to my rescuers and we all made plans to gain revenge on the kly and teach them a lesson in manners.<br>
<br>
&lt;Salvia buys a round of drinks and makes a toast to the bravery of those who saved her&gt;<br>
<br>
&quot;If ever you need help, I will come.  To the darkest jungles and the coldest wastelands I will travel to aide those that saved my life!&quot;<br>
<br>
&lt;Salvia feels the twinge in her arm where the amulet has been.  It has left a nasty little scar that she is ashamed to show.  She makes a mental note to ask Tigonie exactly what the &quot;tears&quot; she has heard about look like&gt; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=14.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.showNextMessage?topicID=14.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=17><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.emailToFriend?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.threadControl?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub101.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option 